    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B11",
      "estimated_duration_s": 11,
      "narration_text": "For an illustrative four-electron-volt barrier, kappa is about 1.02 per ångström. Relative to a five-ångström gap, six ångströms gives about I naught over 7.7, while four gives about 7.7 I naught.",
      "shot": {
